@startuml
actor User
participant NGINX
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "User Service" as UserService

User -> NGINX: POST /auth/login
NGINX -> Gateway: Forward request
Gateway -> UserService: /auth/login
UserService --> Gateway: JWT Token
Gateway --> User: 200 OK + JWT

User -> NGINX: GET /api/users/me (JWT)
NGINX -> Gateway: Forward request
Gateway -> Gateway: Validate JWT
Gateway -> UserService: Forward request
UserService --> Gateway: User data
Gateway --> User: 200 OK
@enduml
